Using polygons as the basic building blocks of our images will allow us to create more realistic images notably
1) we can fill in surfaces to create solids
2) we can calculate what direction a surface is facing

edge Matrix

[p0p1,p1p2,p2p0...]
 e0    e1   e2

polygon matrix
[p0p1p2,p2p3p4]
 t0       t1
 
 
